Using "test.pdb" from here: git/toy_binding/system-setup/ as a template. C12 is the original point {0 0 0}. To rotate the pocket and make it faces up along z axis, the following operations are done using VMD:
1. set sel [atomselect top all]
2. set M [transvecinv {3.246000051498413 0.0 2.00600004196167}]
3. $sel move $M 
4. set M [transaxis y 90]
5. $sel move $M 

